{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 67.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The South of France battle, it wasn't bad till we got some miles inland-- over a hundred miles inland and running into the Vosges Mountains.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Vosges Mountains are very rugged, heavily timbered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- we were running into winter then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The winter descended upon us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a lot of snow and some-- and rain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the weather was very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was very difficult to fight against the-- to attack the German fortified positions because they had time to dig in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we just slogged it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We took casualties every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe in my battalion, I would take a, a mountain-- take me all day to take a mountaintop The next day, I had to do the same thing on the next mountain.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was very discouraging because we took very, very heavy casualties.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the weather was absolutely miserable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the soldiers were miserable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were not getting many replacements in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were getting under strength.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometimes, were in the line for-- fighting for over 60 days with no relief at all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- the American Army was getting stretched pretty thin then because of the advance to our left on the-- from the-- as a result of the Normandy invasion.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were just running short on men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we had the war going on in the Pacific, as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the American Army was stretched pretty thin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a thoroughly miserable and costly campaign that we put on to getting to the German border [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] from our initial landing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lost-- in my regiment alone, we lost several hundred men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lost several hundred in my battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
